          <p class="text-stone-600">Flu shot season? New service? Send targeted messages to your patient list in minutes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Analytics Dashboard</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">See what's working. Track new patients, review scores, and engagement all in one place.</p>
        </div>
